            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzekiel%2018%3A1-19%3A14%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Justice%20of%20a%20Righteous%20God%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20another%20message%20came%20to%20me%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhy%20do%20you%20quote%20this%20proverb%20concerning%20the%20land%20of%20Israel%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BThe%20parents%20have%20eaten%20sour%20grapes%2C%20but%20their%20children%26%23x2019%3Bs%20mouths%20pucker%20at%20the%20taste%26%23x2019%3B%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20surely%20as%20I%20live%2C%20says%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20you%20will%20not%20quote%20this%20proverb%20anymore%20in%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_4%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20all%20people%20are%20mine%20to%20judge%26%23x2014%3Bboth%20parents%20and%20children%20alike.%20And%20this%20is%20my%20rule%3A%20The%20person%20who%20sins%20is%20the%20one%20who%20will%20die.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_5%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSuppose%20a%20certain%20man%20is%20righteous%20and%20does%20what%20is%20just%20and%20right.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_6%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20does%20not%20feast%20in%20the%20mountains%20before%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20idols%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E18%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20Hebrew%20term%20(literally%20%3Cem%3Eround%20things%3C%2Fem%3E)%20probably%20alludes%20to%20dung%3B%20also%20in%2018%3A12%2C%2015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20worship%20them.%20He%20does%20not%20commit%20adultery%20or%20have%20intercourse%20with%20a%20woman%20during%20her%20menstrual%20period.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_7%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20is%20a%20merciful%20creditor%2C%20not%20keeping%20the%20items%20given%20as%20security%20by%20poor%20debtors.%20He%20does%20not%20rob%20the%20poor%20but%20instead%20gives%20food%20to%20the%20hungry%20and%20provides%20clothes%20for%20the%20needy.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_8%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20grants%20loans%20without%20interest%2C%20stays%20away%20from%20injustice%2C%20is%20honest%20and%20fair%20when%20judging%20others%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_9%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20faithfully%20obeys%20my%20decrees%20and%20regulations.%20Anyone%20who%20does%20these%20things%20is%20just%20and%20will%20surely%20live%2C%20says%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_10%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20suppose%20that%20man%20has%20a%20son%20who%20grows%20up%20to%20be%20a%20robber%20or%20murderer%20and%20refuses%20to%20do%20what%20is%20right.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_11%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20that%20son%20does%20all%20the%20evil%20things%20his%20father%20would%20never%20do%26%23x2014%3Bhe%20worships%20idols%20on%20the%20mountains%2C%20commits%20adultery%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_12%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3Eoppresses%20the%20poor%20and%20helpless%2C%20steals%20from%20debtors%20by%20refusing%20to%20let%20them%20redeem%20their%20security%2C%20worships%20idols%2C%20commits%20detestable%20sins%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_13%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20lends%20money%20at%20excessive%20interest.%20Should%20such%20a%20sinful%20person%20live%3F%20No!%20He%20must%20die%20and%20must%20take%20full%20blame.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_14%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20suppose%20that%20sinful%20son%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20a%20son%20who%20sees%20his%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20wickedness%20and%20decides%20against%20that%20kind%20of%20life.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_15%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20son%20refuses%20to%20worship%20idols%20on%20the%20mountains%20and%20does%20not%20commit%20adultery.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_16%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20does%20not%20exploit%20the%20poor%2C%20but%20instead%20is%20fair%20to%20debtors%20and%20does%20not%20rob%20them.%20He%20gives%20food%20to%20the%20hungry%20and%20provides%20clothes%20for%20the%20needy.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_17%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20helps%20the%20poor%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E18%3A17%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20version%20reads%20%3Cem%3EHe%20refuses%20to%20do%20evil.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20does%20not%20lend%20money%20at%20interest%2C%20and%20obeys%20all%20my%20regulations%20and%20decrees.%20Such%20a%20person%20will%20not%20die%20because%20of%20his%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sins%3B%20he%20will%20surely%20live.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_18%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20father%20will%20die%20for%20his%20many%20sins%26%23x2014%3Bfor%20being%20cruel%2C%20robbing%20people%2C%20and%20doing%20what%20was%20clearly%20wrong%20among%20his%20people.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_19%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3B%26%23x2018%3BWhat%3F%26%23x2019%3B%20you%20ask.%20%26%23x2018%3BDoesn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20the%20child%20pay%20for%20the%20parent%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sins%3F%26%23x2019%3B%20No!%20For%20if%20the%20child%20does%20what%20is%20just%20and%20right%20and%20keeps%20my%20decrees%2C%20that%20child%20will%20surely%20live.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_20%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20person%20who%20sins%20is%20the%20one%20who%20will%20die.%20The%20child%20will%20not%20be%20punished%20for%20the%20parent%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sins%2C%20and%20the%20parent%20will%20not%20be%20punished%20for%20the%20child%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sins.%20Righteous%20people%20will%20be%20rewarded%20for%20their%20own%20righteous%20behavior%2C%20and%20wicked%20people%20will%20be%20punished%20for%20their%20own%20wickedness.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_21%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20if%20wicked%20people%20turn%20away%20from%20all%20their%20sins%20and%20begin%20to%20obey%20my%20decrees%20and%20do%20what%20is%20just%20and%20right%2C%20they%20will%20surely%20live%20and%20not%20die.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_22%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20their%20past%20sins%20will%20be%20forgotten%2C%20and%20they%20will%20live%20because%20of%20the%20righteous%20things%20they%20have%20done.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_23%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BDo%20you%20think%20that%20I%20like%20to%20see%20wicked%20people%20die%3F%20says%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Of%20course%20not!%20I%20want%20them%20to%20turn%20from%20their%20wicked%20ways%20and%20live.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_18_24%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EHowever%2C%20if%20righteous%20people%20turn%20from%20their%20righteous%20behavior%20and%20start%20doing%20sinful%20things%20and%20act%20like%20other%20sinners%2C%20should%20they%20be%20allowed%20to%20live%3F%20No%2C%20of%20course%20not!%20All%20their%20righteous%20acts%20will%20be%20forgotten%2C%20and%20they%20will%20die%2